comments: Haliburton (IND) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball defending Westbrook (LAL).
Hield (IND) extends an arm into Davis's (LAL) path and initiates contact to his head that affects his FOM.
Turner (IND) legally contests Westbrook's (LAL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hield (IND) places his hands on Reaves (LAL) with slight extension prior to moving around the screen.
Hield (IND) has a hand placed on Westbrook's (LAL) back as he enters his jump shooting motion and he immediately removes it.
Mathurin (IND) moves alongside of Westbrook's (LAL) path to the basket and legally contests his driving shot attempt.
Both Davis (LAL) and Nembhard (IND) get their hand on the ball while pursuing the rebound and any contact is incidental.
Davis (LAL) jumps along with Nembard (LAL) on his path to the basket and legally contests the shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) moves into Davis's (LAL) space and initiates contact that affects his ability to control the rebound.
Play is stopped as the ball is inbounded to reset the shot clock from 14 to 24.
Hield (IND) firms up in a screening position in Schroder's (LAL) path and does not deliver contact. He briefly places an arm on Schroder's back, but the contact is marginal.
Hield (IND) briefly places an arm around James (LAL) but immediately slides it off and does not affect his ability to receive the pass.
Turner (IND) is actively guarding an opponent within three seconds of entering the lane.
Haliburton (IND) exits the lane within three seconds.
Hield (IND) moves alongside of James (LAL) on his path to the basket and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) reaches across Haliburton's (IND) body and initiates contact to his arm that affects his SQBR.
Haliburton (IND) maintains a legal dribble after gathering the rebound.
James (LAL) legally contests Nembhard's (IND) jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a successful three-point basket by Nembhard (IND) prior to the expiration of the game clock is confirmed.
